Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:34.13,Ichika,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946.286,682.203)}Well then, congratulations on Project Sekai's 5th Anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.02,Ichika,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946.286,682.203)}The four of us playing Leo/need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:38.90,Ichika,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946.286,682.203)}have gathered to record this video message for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.58,Saki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932.572,846.949)}It's finally happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:48.12,Saki,,0,0,0,,We can finally touch each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.96,Ichika,,0,0,0,,This is the first time all four of us are together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:57.96,Saki,,0,0,0,,Wow, the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.16,Saki,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.84,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thank you, 5th Anniversary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:01.72,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Thank you, 5th Anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:04.26,Saki,,0,0,0,,The four of us are really all together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.26,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.26,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:07.26,Shiho,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1593.143,716.526)}I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:10.26,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.857,155.932)}{\fad(600, 0)}Looking Back on These 5 Years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:14.77,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Let's start by taking a look back on these last 5 years of Project Sekai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:17.33,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Anyone have anything burning they need to get out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:19.57,Ichika,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:21.70,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Are we all like your students?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I'm too nervous to start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:27.43,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I guess Ichika is the one who should be starting us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:34.11,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Initially, Ichika tended to speak with a lot of "..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:37.65,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Also lots of monologuing to herself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:43.10,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Like she had lots of things that she wanted to say but didn't know how to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.12,Ichika,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.77,Ichika,,0,0,0,,she kept a lot of things bottled up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:51.39,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But now, after 5 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:54.08,Ichika,,0,0,0,,she's able to more openly express her happiness and joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.77,Ichika,,0,0,0,,and she can speak her mind to her bandmates more freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:59.95,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Like her love for yakisoba bread....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.63,Ichika,,0,0,0,,and when she goes off full throttle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.63,Saki,,0,0,0,,At first I didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:06.57,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't really get that vibe from her at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:09.72,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But she's shaken that off more recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.56,Ichika,,0,0,0,,even if her love for Miku is so great,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.57,Ichika,,0,0,0,,
